snippet.title: Sker Ritual - Teaser | Wishlist Now
snippet.description:
Wishlist and follow now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1492070/?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=tease
Subscribe for updates: https://www.walesinteractive.com/skerritual

The co-op survival FPS and spiritual successor to the award-winning occult horror, Maid of Sker. Play solo or up to 4 players to survive the supernatural onslaught of the Quiet Ones.

Coming to PC Q2 2022 and PS4, PS5, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One later in 2022
